A robbery suspect wanted for more than 10 robberies in Ruaraka has been charged with armed robbery at Makadara Law Courts in Nairobi.
Kelly Ochieng was charged with violently robbing Livingstone Otieno of a mobile phone and Sh500 while armed with a knife during what is said to be a door-to-door robbery in Kasabuni estate on September 12, 2020.



